OL,3,CStalking: Investigating a crime that
OL,4,Cleaves victims living in constant fear
OL,6,FI've reported on stalking before.
OL,8,FI've encountered stalking before.
OL,10,FThe effects of permanently living in
OL,11,Ffear about what's coming next are all-
OL,12,Fconsuming.
OL,14,FAs Jane Harvey from the Hollie Gazzard
OL,15,FTrust put it so well: "If you think
OL,16,Fabout the scariest part of a scary
OL,17,Ffilm it's not when the monster jumps
OL,18,Fout, it's before the monster jumps out
OL,19,Fand that's how victims have explained
OL,20,Fto me stalking makes them feel."
OL,26,@wD@WOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
