FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777299067
OL,3,CStalking: Investigating a crime that
OL,4,Cleaves victims living in constant fear
OL,6,FStalking: What is it and how do you
OL,7,Frecognise the signs?
OL,9,FOn this journey, I met women and men
OL,10,Freclaiming control of their lives who
OL,11,Fwanted to be seen and heard, despite
OL,12,Fthe trauma they'd faced. They shared
OL,13,Ftheir stories in order to help others
OL,14,Facknowledge their own trauma.
OL,16,FI met police officers dedicated to the
OL,17,Fextra training introduced over the
OL,18,Flast couple of years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777299067
OL,3,CStalking: Investigating a crime that
OL,4,Cleaves victims living in constant fear
OL,6,FI met charities providing incredible
OL,7,Fsupport to victims, who are frequently
OL,8,Funcertain about when a situation is
OL,9,F"bad enough" to ask for help.
OL,11,FHowever, I was also met with many
OL,12,Ffrustrations.
OL,14,FFrom victims who were burdened with
OL,15,Fthe responsibility of proving the
OL,16,Fcrime, contacted from prison by their
OL,17,Fjailed stalker or undermined by those
OL,18,Faround them, thereby minimising their
OL,19,Ffear.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
