FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777299067
OL,3,CStalking: Investigating a crime that
OL,4,Cleaves victims living in constant fear
OL,6,FFrom police who were unable to see
OL,7,Fcases through to completion because of
OL,8,Fthe time it can take to get to court,
OL,9,Fas well as those grappling with a
OL,10,Fmulti-tiered law totally reliant on
OL,11,Fdeciding how much fear the victim is
OL,12,Fexperiencing.
OL,14,FAnd from charities, fighting to stay
OL,15,Fafloat while propping up the support
OL,16,Fservices for victims.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
