PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777299067
OL,3,CStalking: Investigating a crime that
OL,4,Cleaves victims living in constant fear
OL,6,FNow, the Government has invested and
OL,7,Fchanges have been made. Victims can
OL,8,Fnow know their stalker's name, and
OL,9,FStalking Protection Orders (SPOs) have
OL,10,Fbeen made more widely available.
OL,12,FPolice have made huge changes to the
OL,13,Fway they deal with stalking, from
OL,14,Ftraining to focus groups - but it's
OL,15,Fnot consistent. The phrase 'postcode
OL,16,Flottery' was prevalent in many
OL,17,Fconversations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
